  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Chop your <strong>waxy potatoes</strong> (skins on) into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for an initial 15 min or until starting to brown</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "image": "/images/instructions/chorizo-and-crispy-potato-salad-with-honey-mustard-dressing/step-1.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Tear your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> into chunky bite-sized pieces</p><p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "image": "/images/instructions/chorizo-and-crispy-potato-salad-with-honey-mustard-dressing/step-2.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>halved tomatoes</strong> and <strong>torn ciabatta</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>sliced shallot</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and your <strong>diced chorizo</strong></p><p>Add 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Squeeze the <strong>halved tomatoes</strong> together with the <strong>torn ciabatta </strong>so that the juice soaks into the ciabatta – this is your <strong>marinated ciabatta</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "image": "/images/instructions/chorizo-and-crispy-potato-salad-with-honey-mustard-dressing/step-3.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes have been in the oven for 15 min, remove the tray[s] from the oven and surround them with the <strong>marinated ciabatta</strong></p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for a further 15 min or until the potatoes and the marinated ciabatta is golden and crispy – these are your <strong>roasted potatoes</strong> and <strong>tomato & chorizo croutons</strong></p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk so they don't burn!</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "image": "/images/instructions/chorizo-and-crispy-potato-salad-with-honey-mustard-dressing/step-4.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>wholegrain mustard</strong> and the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> in a bowl with your <strong>honey</strong>, 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a small pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Mix everything together – this is your <strong>honey mustard dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "image": "/images/instructions/chorizo-and-crispy-potato-salad-with-honey-mustard-dressing/step-5.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>avocado[s]</strong> in half lengthways, around the stone[s]</p><p>Remove the <strong>stone[s]</strong> using a teaspoon, scoop out the <strong>avocado flesh</strong> and roughly chop</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into wedges</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "image": "/images/instructions/chorizo-and-crispy-potato-salad-with-honey-mustard-dressing/step-6.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Once the roasted potatoes<strong> </strong>and tomato & chorizo croutons are golden, transfer them to a bowl</p><p>Add the <strong>honey mustard dressing</strong>, <strong>salad</strong> and <strong>chopped avocado</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>chorizo & crispy potato salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "image": "/images/instructions/chorizo-and-crispy-potato-salad-with-honey-mustard-dressing/step-7.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>chorizo & crispy potato salad</strong> and season with a crack of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8
    }
  ],
